---
import CTAButton from "./CTAButton.astro";

const metrics = [
  { label: "1 niş: sadece klima firmaları", href: "#sistem" },
  { label: "Büyümek isteyen firmalar", href: "#basvuru" },
  { label: "100 mesaj hedefi şeffaflığı", href: "#100-mesaj" },
  { label: "WhatsApp odaklı akış", href: "#basvuru" },
];

const serviceTags = ["Bakım", "Temizlik", "Arıza", "Montaj"];
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden pb-20 pt-16 md:pb-28 md:pt-24">
  <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-24 -z-10 h-72 w-72 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-lime/20 blur-[120px]"></div>
  <div class="section-shell grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.04fr_0.96fr]">
    <div>
      <p class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-lime/30 bg-lime/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-extrabold uppercase text-lime">
        Sadece klima firmalarına özel reklam sistemi
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-balance mt-7 text-4xl font-black leading-[1.05] text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-7xl">
        Klima Firmaları İçin Düzenli
        <span class="bg-lime-gradient bg-clip-text text-transparent">Potansiyel Müşteri Akışı</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-7 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-textMuted">
        İklimDijital, klima bakım, temizlik, montaj ve arıza hizmetleri sunan firmalar için Meta Ads odaklı müşteri kazanım sistemi kurar.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-white/70">
        Reklam bütçenizi rastgele harcatmak yerine, hizmet türüne ve bölgeye göre ölçülebilir mesaj akışı kurarız.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-9 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
        <CTAButton label="WhatsApp'tan Bilgi Al" class="w-full sm:w-auto" />
        <CTAButton href="#basvuru" label="Başvuru Yap" variant="secondary" class="w-full sm:w-auto" />
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
        {metrics.map((metric) => (
          <a href={metric.href} class="group rounded-[8px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.035] px-4 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white/80 transition hover:border-lime/40 hover:bg-lime/10 hover:text-white focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-lime">
            {metric.label}
            <span class="ml-2 text-lime opacity-0 transition group-hover:opacity-100" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="glass-panel relative rounded-[8px] p-5 md:p-7">
      <div class="absolute -right-10 -top-10 h-36 w-36 rounded-full bg-lime/20 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="mb-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/10 pb-5">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-textMuted">Kampanya</p>
            <h2 class="mt-1 text-xl font-black text-white">Klima Bakım / Temizlik</h2>
          </div>
          <span class="rounded-full border border-lime/30 bg-lime/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-extrabold text-lime">
            WhatsApp Mesaj
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {serviceTags.map((tag) => (
            <a href="#basvuru" class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.05] px-3 py-2 text-xs font-bold text-white/80 transition hover:border-lime/40 hover:bg-lime/10 hover:text-white">{tag}</a>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-[8px] border border-white/10 bg-[#151515] p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-textMuted">Gelen Mesajlar</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-3xl font-black text-white">Takip</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-bold text-lime">Düzenli akış</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-[8px] border border-white/10 bg-[#151515] p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-textMuted">Mesaj Başına Maliyet</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-3xl font-black text-white">Takip</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-bold text-lime">Optimize edilir</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-[8px] border border-white/10 bg-[#151515] p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-textMuted">En İyi Hizmet Açısı</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-2xl font-black text-white">Veriye göre</p>
            <div class="mt-4 h-2 rounded-full bg-white/10">
              <div class="h-2 w-3/4 rounded-full bg-lime"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-[8px] border border-white/10 bg-[#151515] p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-textMuted">Devam Önerisi</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-2xl font-black text-white">Bütçe yönü</p>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-end gap-2">
              <span class="h-6 flex-1 rounded-t bg-white/[0.12]"></span>
              <span class="h-10 flex-1 rounded-t bg-lime/45"></span>
              <span class="h-14 flex-1 rounded-t bg-lime"></span>
              <span class="h-8 flex-1 rounded-t bg-white/[0.18]"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-5 text-xs leading-6 text-textMuted">
          Bu alan temsili görünüm sunar. Gerçek sonuçlar şehir, bütçe, sezon, kreatif ve hizmet bölgesine göre değişebilir.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
